-family-goop-2025-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhen%20They%20Spotted%20Us...%26quot%3B%3A%20Nurse%20Who%20Saved%2020%20Pregnant%20Women%20During%2026%2F11%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20extradition%20of%2026%2F11%20plotter%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20has%20ripped%20the%20band-aid%20off%20the%20wounds%20of%20many%20who%20lived%20through%20the%20three-day%20mayhem%20in%20Mumbai%2016%20years%20ago.%20For%20others%2C%20it%20was%20an%20occasion%20to%20remember%20the%20massive%20pressure%20they%20came%20under%20to%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20others%20--%20at%20great%20risk%20to%20themselves.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20hero%20is%20nurse%20Anjali%20Kulthe%2C%20who%20managed%20to%20save%2020%20pregnant%20women%20admitted%20at%20Mumbai's%20Cama%20hospital%20and%20ensured%20safe%20delivery%20for%20one%20of%20them%20--%20a%20high-risk%20patient%20of%20hypertension.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%209.30%20pm%20on%20November%2026%2C%20when%20they%20got%20information%20that%20terrorists%20who%20were%20attacking%20the%20CST%20station%20were%20moving%20towards%20the%20Cama%20hospital%2C%20Ms%20Kulthe%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview.%20Minutes%20later%2C%20they%20heard%20gunshots%20from%20a%20lane%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20out%20of%20the%20window%2C%20we%20could%20see%20two%20terrorists%20running%20and%20the%20police%20firing%20at%20them.%20Then%20the%20terrorists%20vaulted%20over%20the%20low%20gate%20and%20entered%20the%20hospital%20premises.%20I%20saw%20they%20had%20shot%20the%20two%20security%20guards%2C%20who%20were%20lying%20in%20a%20heap.%20When%20they%20spotted%20us%20at%20the%20window%2C%20they%20opened%20fire%20at%20us%20and%20one%20of%20our%20workers%20got%20injured.%20I%20took%20her%20to%20the%20casualty%20and%20informed%20everyone%20that%20the%20terrorists%20had%20entered%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20her%20return%2C%20the%20nurse%20shut%20the%20main%20doors%20of%20the%20ward%20and%20took%20the%2020%20patients%20to%20a%2010x10%20pantry.%20Cellphones%20and%20lights%20were%20switched%20off%20and%20they%20sat%20in%20the%20dark.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20the%20hypertension%20patient%20started%20getting%20labour%20pain.%20The%20doctor%20refused%20to%20come%20to%20the%20ward%2C%20for%20by%20now%2C%20the%20gunbattle%20was%20raging%20inside%20the%20hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kulthe%20said%20she%20took%20the%20patient%20to%20the%20labour%20room%20by%20the%20staircase%2C%20going%20up%20one%20step%20at%20a%20time%2C%20staying%20close%20to%20the%20wall.%20%C2%A0By%20the%20morning%2C%20she%20had%20given%20birth%20to%20a%20baby%20girl%2C%20who%20was%20named%20'Goli'%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20that%20night%2C%20Ms%20Kulthe%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20was%20under%20attack%20for%20five%20hours%20that%20night.%20Besides%20the%20two%20security%20guards%2C%20one%20more%20hospital%20worker%20died.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20she%20had%20got%20over%20the%20fear%20and%20trauma%20of%20that%20night%2C%20Ms%20Kulthe%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20single%20one%20of%20us%20who%20worked%20at%20the%20hospital%20-%20doctors%2C%20nurses%20or%20other%20staff%20--%20will%20ever%20forget%20that%20night%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20they%20threw%20hand%20grenades%2C%20opened%20fire%2C%20killed%20people%2C%20none%20of%20us%20can%20ever%20forget%20it.%20For%20the%20whole%20country%2C%20it%20was%20a%20night%20of%20sadness%20and%20horror%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETahawwur%20Rana%2C%20who%20was%20extradited%2C%20is%20accused%20of%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20the%202008%20attacks%20that%20cost%20166%20lives.%20Pakistani-American%20terrorist%20and%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20said%20Rana%20had%20extended%20logistical%20and%20financial%20support%20for%20the%20terror%20operation.%20He%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20murder%20and%20forgery%20and%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-day%20attack%20that%20devastated%20India's%20financial%20capital%20in%202008%20had%20seen%20hotels%2C%20a%20train%20station%2C%20a%20Jewish%20center%2C%20and%20other%20spots%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2010%20terrorists%20who%20took%20part%20in%20the%20attack%2C%20only%20one%2C%20Ajmal%20Kasab%2C%20was%20caught%20alive%20and%20was%20hanged%20on%20November%2021%2C%202012.%20India%20has%20said%20Pakistan-based%20terror%20group%20%C2%A0Lashkar-e-Taiba%20had%20orchestrated%20the%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744345740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fg5gtinto_2611-nurse-cama-hospital_625x300_10_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-rana-extradition-they-opened-fire-nurse-who-saved-20-pregnant-women-during-26-11-attacks-8135620%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20extradition%20of%2026%2F11%20plotter%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20has%20ripped%20the%20band-aid%20off%20the%20wounds%20of%20many%20who%20lived%20through%20the%20three-day%20mayhem%20in%20Mumbai%2016%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tahawwur%20Rana's%20Interrogation%3A%20Key%20Questions%20He%20May%20Be%20Asked%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20special%20plane%20touched%20down%20in%20Delhi%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20a%20team%20from%20the%20anti-terror%20body%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%2C%20flanked%20by%20elite%20National%20Security%20Guard%20(NSG)%20commandos%2C%20escorted%20Tahawwur%20Hussain%20Rana%20-%20the%20Pakistani-origin%20Canadian%20national%20accused%20of%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20-%20to%20a%20court%20where%20he%20was%20formally%20remanded%20to%2018-day%20NIA%20custody.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20hours%2C%20he%20was%20moved%20under%20high%20security%20to%20the%20anti-terror%20agency's%20heavily%20guarded%20headquarters%20at%20the%20CGO%20complex.%20Rana%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20under%20a%20US%20extradition%20warrant%20and%20had%20exhausted%20every%20available%20legal%20avenue%20to%20avoid%20facing%20Indian%20justice%2C%20will%20now%20be%20probed%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInside%20Rana's%20Interrogation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20Rana%20has%20been%20kept%20in%20a%2014x14%20cell%20on%20the%20ground%20floor%20of%20the%20NIA%20headquarters.%20This%20cell%20is%20equipped%20with%20CCTV%20cameras%2C%20a%20bed%20and%20a%20toilet.%20Multiple%20layers%20of%20digital%20security%20has%20been%20placed%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20retinue%20of%2024-hour%20guards.%20Only%2012%20NIA%20officials%20are%20allowed%20to%20enter%20this%20cell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2010%20am%20today%2C%20the%20first%20round%20of%20interrogation%20begins.%20Inside%20a%20sealed%2C%20CCTV-monitored%20interrogation%20room%2C%20equipped%20with%20video-recording%20equipment%2C%20a%20team%20led%20by%20NIA%20officers%20of%20Superintendent%20and%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20rank%20will%20begin%20the%20probe.%20A%20daily%20interrogation%20diary%20will%20be%20maintained%2C%20detailing%20every%20exchange%20and%20answer.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%2018-day%20custody%20period%2C%20a%20comprehensive%20disclosure%20statement%20-%20legally%20admissible%20-%20will%20be%20prepared%20as%20part%20of%20the%20case%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana's%20legal%20team%20in%20the%20US%20had%20cited%20multiple%20life-threatening%20medical%20conditions%20-%20including%20chronic%20asthma%2C%20Parkinson's%20disease%2C%20heart%20ailments%2C%20suspected%20bladder%20cancer%2C%20and%20cognitive%20decline%20-%20in%20a%20last-ditch%20attempt%20to%20block%20his%20extradition.%20They%20warned%20that%20Indian%20custody%20would%20effectively%20amount%20to%20a%20death%20sentence.%20But%20both%20the%20US%20federal%20courts%20and%20ultimately%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20rejected%20the%20argument%2C%20clearing%20the%20path%20for%20his%20return%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20medical%20check-up%20will%20be%20administered%20every%2048%20hours%20to%20monitor%20his%20health%20and%20ensure%20compliance%20with%20human%20rights%20standards.%20Special%20precautions%20are%20being%20taken%20to%20prevent%20any%20possibility%20of%20self-harm%20in%20case%20Rana%20attempts%20to%20escape%20accountability%20by%20compromising%20his%20safety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEstablishing%20Identity%20and%20Intent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20the%20first%20leg%20of%20Rana's%20interrogation%20will%20focus%20on%20his%20personal%20and%20familial%20background.%20Investigators%20will%20probe%20details%20about%20his%20upbringing%2C%20education%2C%20family%2C%20and%20career%2C%20including%20his%20transition%20from%20a%20trained%20medical%20doctor%20to%20an%20alleged%20conspirator%20in%20international%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20particular%2C%20they%20will%20ask%20why%20he%20brought%20his%20wife%20with%20him%20during%20his%202008%20visit%20to%20India.%20Did%20his%20family%20know%20about%20his%20alleged%20links%20to%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%20-%20another%20accused%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%20case%2C%20who%20is%20currently%20in%20jail%20in%20the%20US%20-%20or%20his%20role%20in%20planning%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E26%2F11%20Mumbai%20Attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20and%20most%20critical%20rounds%20of%20interrogation%20will%20focus%20squarely%20on%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%20-%20a%20series%20of%20coordinated%20shootings%20and%20bombings%20carried%20out%20by%20ten%20terrorists%20of%20the%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20terror%20group%20that%20left%20166%20people%20dead%20and%20more%20than%20238%20injured%20over%20four%20harrowing%20days.%20Rana%20is%20accused%20of%20facilitating%20reconnaissance%20missions%2C%20aiding%20Headley's%20fake%20visa%20applications%2C%20and%20liaising%20with%20LeT%20terrorists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccording%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20among%20the%20key%20questions%20that%20will%20be%20put%20to%20him%20are%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhere%20was%20he%20physically%20located%20on%20November%2026%2C%202008%2C%20when%20the%20attacks%20began%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhy%20did%20he%20travel%20to%20India%20between%20November%208%20and%20November%2021%20of%20that%20year%3F%20Where%20did%20he%20go%2C%20and%20whom%20did%20he%20meet%20during%20this%20window%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhen%20did%20he%20first%20learn%20about%20the%20impending%20Mumbai%20attacks%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20was%20the%20extent%20of%20his%20relationship%20with%20David%20Headley%2C%20and%20why%20did%20he%20help%20procure%20a%20fake%20visa%20for%20him%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20kind%20of%20information%20did%20Headley%20relay%20to%20Rana%20during%20his%20visits%20to%20India%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20was%20the%20nature%20of%20Rana's%20conversations%20with%20Headley%3F%20Did%20they%20involve%20detailed%20planning%20of%20the%20attacks%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20direct%20or%20indirect%20role%20did%20Rana%20play%20in%20selecting%20and%20surveilling%20potential%20targets%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHow%20did%20he%20assist%20Headley%20in%20gathering%20actionable%20intelligence%20for%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWas%20he%20involved%20in%20any%20logistical%20planning%20or%20funding%20of%20the%20operation%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20he%20liaise%20with%20operatives%20beyond%20Headley%20-%20including%20individuals%20embedded%20in%20the%20LeT%20and%20Pakistan's%20ISI%20network%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cstrong%3ELashkar-e-Taiba%20Connection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%2C%20the%20interrogation%20will%20pivot%20to%20Rana's%20alleged%20links%20with%20Lashkar-e-Taiba.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20officials%20want%20to%20determine%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHow%20and%20when%20did%20he%20meet%20LeT%20chief%20Hafiz%20Saeed%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20was%20the%20nature%20of%20their%20relationship%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDid%20he%20provide%20logistical%20or%20financial%20support%20to%20Lashkar%3F%20If%20so%2C%20what%20did%20the%20group%20provide%20in%20return%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECan%20Rana%20identify%20other%20members%20of%20the%20LeT%20by%20name%2C%20face%2C%20or%20role%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20is%20his%20understanding%20of%20the%20LeT's%20hierarchy%2C%20recruitment%20methods%2C%20and%20funding%20sources%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWho%20supplies%20the%20group's%20weaponry%2C%20and%20which%20countries%20are%20allegedly%20involved%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20role%20do%20the%20Pakistani%20Army%20and%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI)%20play%20in%20training%2C%20funding%2C%20and%20selecting%20targets%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDoes%20Rana%20have%20knowledge%20of%20training%20camps%20run%20by%20LeT%20and%20HuJI%20(Harkat-ul-Jihad-al-Islami)%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHow%20many%20ISI%20officers%20are%20involved%20in%20this%20process%2C%20and%20what%20exactly%20is%20taught%20during%20these%20training%20modules%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWho%20makes%20the%20final%20decisions%20about%20executing%20attacks%3F%20Are%20instructions%20relayed%20directly%20by%20ISI%20officers%20or%20routed%20through%20LeT%20intermediaries%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWhat%20psychological%20conditioning%20is%20employed%20to%20ready%20young%20men%20for%20suicide%20missions%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHow%20many%20individuals%20are%20involve