%204.5%20per%20cent.%20The%20continued%20uncertainty%20surrounding%20global%20trade%20policy%20weighed%20heavily%20on%20investor%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20rising%20market%20volatility%2C%20gold%20prices%20in%20India%20surged%20to%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%20Rs91%2C500%20per%2010%20grams%20as%20investors%20turned%20to%20safe-haven%20assets.%20The%20Japanese%20yen%20and%20Swiss%20franc%20also%20saw%20increased%20inflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Dollar%20Index%20(DXY)%20fell%20to%20100%2C%20which%20could%20eventually%20benefit%20emerging%20markets%2C%20but%20analysts%20warned%20that%20sentiment%20remains%20fragile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20corporate%20front%2C%20Tata%20Consultancy%20Services%20(TCS)%20reported%20earnings%20below%20market%20expectations%2C%20leading%20several%20brokerages%20to%20slash%20their%20target%20prices%20for%20the%20IT%20giant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20global%20concerns%2C%20a%20White%20House%20official%20confirmed%20that%20China's%20average%20tariff%20rate%20would%20rise%20to%20145%20per%20cent%2C%20further%20intensifying%20trade%20tensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20uncertainty%20looming%20large%2C%20experts%20are%20advising%20investors%20to%20proceed%20with%20caution%20despite%20the%20short-term%20rally%20in%20equities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744344360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fsagi8q7g_sensex_625x300_04_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fsensex-gains-over-1-000-points-after-donald-trump-pauses-tariffs-for-90-days-8137489%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BSE%20Sensex%20jumped%201%2C061.26%20points%20to%20open%20at%2074%2C941.53%2C%20while%20the%20NSE%20Nifty%20climbed%20354.90%20points%2C%20starting%20the%20day%20at%2022%2C7