ving%20the%20wilderness%20when%20a%20pair%20of%20scientists%20and%20a%20guide%20stumbled%20upon%20their%20bloody%20bacchanal%2C%20keeping%20the%20group%20from%20mutiny%20will%20also%20be%20a%20challenge.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20curious%20to%20see%20how%20long%20she%20can%20hold%20that%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20N%C3%A9lisse%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229dfdbe08-58ae-4931-8b08-21e4ad82279a%5C%22%3EN%C3%A9lisse%20thinks%20Shauna%20is%20bisexual%2C%20but%20she's%20not%20sure%20Shauna%20and%20Jackie%20were%20more%20than%20friends%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jackie%20(Ella%20Purnell)%20crosses%20her%20arms%20confronting%20teen%20Shauna%20in%20a%20supermarket%20in%20a%20flashback%20on%20season%203%20of%20%26quot%3BYellowjackets.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f6b10fc6ad288d147daf80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGhost%20Jackie%20(Ella%20Purnell)%20makes%20a%20few%20appearances%20this%20season.%3Cp%3EKailey%20Schwerman%2FParamount%2B%20with%20SHOWTIME%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20subtler%20apparent%20revelations%20in%20the%20finale%20happens%20when%20a%20drunken%20Travis%20confronts%20Shauna%20before%20the%20girls%20leave%20to%20hunt%20down%20Mari.%20He%20tells%20her%20that%20%26quot%3Bnone%20of%20this%20is%20even%20real.%26quot%3B%20He%20suggests%20that%20he's%20experiencing%20the%20thoughts%20of%20those%20who%20have%20died%20there%2C%20including%20his%20younger%20brother%20Javi%20and%20Shauna's%20dead%20best%20friend%20Jackie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETravis%20tells%20Shauna%20that%20Jackie's%20thoughts%20are%20his%20favorite%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20slumber%20party%20makeouts%3F%20The%20jealousy%3F%20The%20betrayal%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhether%20that%20was%20a%20drug-induced%20hallucination%20or%20not%2C%20it%20certainly%20seems%20to%20suggest%20that%20something%20sexual%20went%20down%20between%20Shauna%20and%20Jackie%2C%20further%20complicating%20a%20relationship%20that%20was%20already%20complicated%20by%20Shauna's%20affair%20with%20Jackie's%20boyfriend%20Jeff%2C%20who%20ultimately%20married%20Shauna%20and%20has%20a%20daughter%2C%20Callie%2C%20with%20her.%20That%2C%20paired%20with%20the%20season%20three%20storyline%20that%20sees%20Shauna%20embark%20on%20a%20toxic%20relationship%20with%20fellow%20survivor%20Melissa%2C%20is%20pretty%20strong%20evidence%20that%20Shauna%20and%20Jackie%20probably%20hooked%20up%20at%20one%20point%20before%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20brought%20it%20up%20to%20N%C3%A9lisse%2C%20she%20seemed%20surprised%20by%20that%20reading%20of%20the%20moment.%20She%20said%20she%20didn't%20take%20it%20that%20way%20but%20loved%20the%20theory.%20Though%20she%20tries%20to%20avoid%20looking%20at%20TikToks%20of%20the%20show%2C%20she's%20well%20aware%20that%20many%20viewers%20think%20there%20was%20something%20more%20than%20friendship%20between%20Shauna%20and%20Jackie%2C%20at%20least%20on%20Shauna's%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20an%20answer%2C%20actually%2C%20for%20that%20one.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20been%20hinting%20that%20there%20was%20sexuality%20between%20Jackie%20and%20Shauna%2C%26quot%3B%20N%C3%A9lisse%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20creators%20seemed%2C%20from%20our%20discussion%2C%20to%20say%20that%20there%20wasn't%2C%20but%20that%20there%20is%20just%20this%20really%20complex%20relationship.%20It's%20such%20a%20fine%20line%20to%20walk%20on.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20up%20to%20people's%20interpretation%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22585acd83-9f75-44a8-94f6-35421f108ef4%5C%22%3EN%C3%A9lisse%20has%20no%20idea%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20Shauna%20in%20'Yellowjackets'%20season%204%2C%20but%20she%20has%20some%20hopes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20N%C3%A9lisse%2C%20the%20cast%20only%20gets%20the%20scripts%20for%20an%20episode%20about%20a%20week%20before%20filming.%20That%20means%20they're%20not%20privy%20to%20the%20long%20game%20the%20show%20is%20playing%20in%20advance%20of%20individual%20revelations%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20the%20answers%20to%20ongoing%20mysteries%20like%20what's%20going%20on%20with%20Taissa%20and%20whether%20there%20is%20actually%20something%20supernatural%20in%20the%20wilderness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20season%20has%20felt%20almost%20like%20a%20complete%20different%20character%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20N%C3%A9lisse%20said%20of%20playing%20Shauna.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20what's%20fun%20is%20that%20I%20get%20to%20play%20somewhat%20of%20the%20villain%20%5Bin%20season%20three%5D%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20with%20all%20of%20her%20background%20and%20all%20of%20her%20trauma%20and%20all%20of%20her%20luggage%20that%20she's%20been%20carrying.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EN%C3%A9lisse%20says%20Shauna's%20baggage%20helped%20her%20contextualize%20some%20of%20her%20character's%20less%20popular%20decisions.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAlthough%20everything%20that%20she%20does%20is%20maybe%20not%20excusable%2C%20you%20understand%20the%20why%20behind%20it.%20So%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20empathy%20for%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20been%20just%20really%20fun%20to%20be%20able%20to%20tap%20into%20something%20a%20lot%20darker.%20But%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20still%20caring%20for%20her%20and%20rooting%20for%20her%2C%20in%20a%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20can%20Shauna%20go%20any%20darker%20in%20a%20not-yet-confirmed%20season%20four%3F%20N%C3%A9lisse%20isn't%20sure%2C%20but%20she%20kind%20of%20hopes%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20me%20wants%20her%20to%20go%20even%20crazier%2C%20but%20I'm%20like%2C%20she%20needs%20to%20calm%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20%26quot%3BYellowjackets%26quot%3B%20season%20three%20finale%20is%20now%20streaming%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.inside