rrying%20Rana%20landed%20in%20Delhi%20last%20evening%2C%20soon%20after%20he%20exhausted%20all%20legal%20avenues%20to%20stop%20his%20extradition.%20He%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20anti-terror%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkey-conspirator-behind-2008-mayhem-anti-terror-agency-nias-first-statement-on-tahawwur-rana-extradition-8133570%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Investigation%20Agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20(NIA)%20for%2018%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%2C%20a%20Canadian%20national%20of%20Pakistani%20origin%2C%20had%20earlier%20worked%20as%20a%20doctor%20for%20the%20Pakistan%20Army.%20He%20is%20facing%20charges%20for%20his%20role%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20in%20which%20over%20160%20people%20died.%20According%20to%20officials%2C%20he%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20terror%20attack%20and%20was%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20terrorist%20groups%20and%20their%20leaders%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana's%20involvement%20in%20the%20conspiracy%20behind%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%20was%20revealed%20by%20his%20childhood%20friend%20and%20a%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%20-%20who%20said%20he%20was%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20Rana%20and%20even%20took%20his%20permission%20to%20open%20a%20business%20office%20in%20Mumbai%20as%20a%20front%20for%20his%20activities.%20During%20interrogation%2C%20Headley%20had%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20travelled%20to%20India%20five%20times%20between%202007%20and%202008%20and%20done%20recce%20for%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%20-%20using%20a%20five-year%20visa%20that%20Rana%20had%20helped%20him%20obtain.%20He%20also%20revealed%20the%20role%20of%20terror%20group%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%20and%20said%20he%20had%20opened%20an%20immigration%20company%20to%20hide%20his%20identity%20with%20Rana's%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20had%20also%20visited%20Mumbai%20with%20his%20wife%20and%20stayed%20at%20the%20Taj%20Mahal%20Hotel%2C%20which%20became%20a%20target%20of%20the%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013%2C%20Rana%20was%20sentenced%20to%2014%20years%20in%20jail%20but%20was%20released%20in%202020%20on%20health%20grounds.%20He%20was%20re-arrested%20later%20that%20year%20after%20India's%20extradition%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744337580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fnrqaktf4_modi_625x300_11_April_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-2011-post-on-tahawwur-rana-goes-viral-after-his-extradition-8137061%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tahawwwur%20Rana%20landed%20in%20Delhi%20last%20evening%20and%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20custody%20of%20the%20anti-terror%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20for%2018%20days.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modis-2011-post-on-tahawwur-rana-goes-viral-after-his-extradition-8137061%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThat%20Is%20Not%20Acceptable%26quot%3B%3A%20Fuming%20Rajat%20Patidar%20Puts%20Blame%20Of%20Defeat%20On...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERoyal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20skipper%20Rajat%20Patidar%20was%20not%20amused%20with%20the%20way%20his%20batters%20threw%20away%20their%20wickets%20in%20a%20heap%20when%20thing%20were%20cruise%20control%2C%20saying%20this%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20acceptable%26quot%3B%20following%20a%20six-wicket%20home%20loss%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Capitals%20on%20Thursday.%20Spinners%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20and%20Vipraj%20Nigam%20bowled%20with%20purpose%20while%20KL%20Rahul%20struck%20an%20unbeaten%2093%20as%20the%20DC%20juggernaut%20continued%20to%20roll%20menacingly%2C%20inflicting%20a%20morale-shattering%20defeat%20on%20RCB%20with%2013%20balls%20to%20spare.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20not%20batted%20well.%20Batters%20are%20in%20a%20good%20frame%20of%20mind%2C%20they%20have%20shown%20nice%20intent.%2060%20for%20one%2C%20and%20then%2090%20for%20four%2C%20that%20is%20not%20acceptable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patidar%20post%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERCB's%20Phil%20Salt%20had%20pummelled%20the%20DC%20bowlers%20in%20powerplay%20overs%2C%20guiding%20the%20home%20side%20to%2061%2F1%20in%20only%20the%20fourth%20over%20before%20they%20slumped%20to%2091%2F4%20after%20which%20they%20lost%20momentum%20to%20score%20a%20below-par%20163%2F7.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20a%20nice%20batting%20track.%20We%20were%20lacking%20in%20assessing%20the%20conditions%20and%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patidar%2C%20adding%20that%20Tim%20David%20(37)%20did%20his%20bit%20by%20accelerating%20the%20run-scoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20came%20too%20late%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20David%20accelerated%20at%20the%20end%2C%20it%20was%20really%20amazing.%20The%20powerplay%2C%20the%20way%20the%20(RCB)%20fast%20bowlers%20bowled%2C%20it%20was%20really%20special%20(reducing%20DC%20to%2030%2F3)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPlayer%20of%20the%20Match%20KL%20Rahul%20said%20watching%20the%20ball%20keenly%20behind%20the%20stumps%20helped%20him%20when%20he%20came%20in%20to%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20slightly%20tricky%20wicket%20but%20what%20helped%20me%20was%20being%20behind%20the%20stumps%20for%2020%20overs%2C%20watching%20how%20the%20wicket%20played.%20The%20ball%20sat%20in%20the%20wicket%20but%20it%20was%20consistent%20throughout%2C%20it%20was%20one-paced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20what%20my%20shots%20are%2C%20wanted%20to%20get%20off%20to%20a%20good%20start%2C%20and%20then%20assess%20it%20accordingly.%20It%20depends%20on%20the%20conditions%20and%20the%20ground%20and%20the%20dimensions.%20On%20a%20wicket%20like%20this%2C%20I%20knew%20what%20my%20pockets%20were.%20If%20I%20wanted%20to%20hit%20a%20big%20six%2C%20I%20knew%20what%20pockets%20to%20target%2C%20and%20'keeping%20gave%20me%20a%20feeler%20for%20where%20other%20batters%20were%20dismissed%20and%20where%20they%20hit%20the%20sixes%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Rahul.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahul%20added%20that%20having%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket%20in%20his%20formative%20years%20at%20the%20M%20Chinnaswamy%20Stadium%20helped%20him%20immensely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20my%20ground%2C%20my%20home%2C%20(I)%20know%20this%20(ground)%20better%20than%20anyone%20else.%20Something%20I%20have%20always%20done%20with%20my%20preparation%20is%20that%20I%20always%20try%20to%20adapt%20to%20different%20wickets%20(even%20in%20practice).%20I%20experiment%20in%20practice%2C%20get%20out%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20but%20it%20gives%20me%20a%20fair%20idea%20of%20the%20areas%20I%20can%20target%20%E2%80%94%20where%20I%20can%20take%20singles%2C%20where%20I%20can%20hit%20sixes.%26quot%3B%20DC%20skipper%20Axar%20Patel%20said%20four%20wins%20in%20four%20matches%20had%20given%20the%20team%20a%20huge%20boost%20in%20morale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20is%20playing%20with%20confidence%2C%20it%20feels%20nice%20(to%20have%20won%20four%20out%20of%20four).%20We%20talk%20about%20match-ups%20and%20what%20is%20happening%20off%20the%20surface.%20I%20felt%20they%20like%20to%20face%20pacers%2C%20so%20tried%20to%20hold%20them%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20the%20ball%20was%20spinning%20and%20bouncing%2C%20so%20thought%20of%20bowling%20spin%20in%20the%20powerplay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20lauded%20Rahul's%20efforts%20saying%20the%20charismatic%20'keeper-batter%20had%20played%20a%20mature%20innings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20becomes%20a%20very%20easy%20job%20for%20me.%20I%20have%20been%20in%20that%20situation%2C%20being%20used%20as%20a%20floater%20in%20pressure%20situations.%20It%20is%20not%20easy%20(changing%20positions).%20Having%20a%20player%20like%20him%20is%20a%20very%20good%20thing.%20I%20played%20a%20bad%20shot%20today%2