a.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Flaapataa-ladies-fame-nitanshi-goel-wins-heart-as-she-pauses-her-ramp-walk-to-touch-hema-malinis-feet-hugs-sushmita-sen%2Farticleshow%2F120176334.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Donald%20Trump%20Now%20A%20'Supervillain'%20In%20Canadian%20Comic%2C%20Elon%20Musk%20His%20Sidekick%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20world%20has%20heard%20of%20Donald%20Trump%20the%20businessman%2C%20then%20came%20Donald%20Trump%20the%20President%2C%20but%20amid%20growing%20resentment%20in%20Canada%2C%20the%20US%20President%20emerged%20in%20a%20new%20avatar%20-%20a%20supervillain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20repeated%20threats%20to%20annex%20Canada%20and%20make%20it%20the%2051st%20state%20of%20the%20United%20States%20followed%20by%20his%20move%20to%20unleash%20punishing%20tariffs%20have%20breathed%20new%20life%20into%20a%20superhero%20from%20the%201970s%20-%20Captain%20Canuck%2C%20Canada's%20version%20of%20Captain%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Canadian%20superhero%2C%20cloaked%20in%20a%20red-and-white%20bodysuit%20and%20a%20face%20mask%20featuring%20the%20maple%20leaf%20-%20a%20prominent%20symbol%20of%20Canada%2C%20is%20a%20government%20agent%20with%20superhuman%20strength%2C%20whose%20mission%20is%20to%20save%20Canada%20and%20defend%20the%20nation's%20sovereignty%20from%20the%20'bad%20guys'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20Captain%20Canuck's%20resurgence%2C%2074-year-old%20Richard%20Comely%2C%20the%20artist%20who%20co-created%20the%20comic%20book%20character%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20a%20sudden%20Canadians%20are%20looking%20to%20Captain%20Canuck%20as%20a%20symbol.%20And%20it's%20basically%2C%20to%20them%2C%20Captain%20Canuck%20symbolizes%20independence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20annexation%20threats%20and%20tariffs%20have%20breathed%20new%20life%20into%20a%20superhero%20from%20the%201970s%20%E2%80%94%20Captain%20Canuck%2C%20a%20Mountie%20with%20superhuman%20strength%20who%20defends%20Canada's%20sovereignty%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fisx9L3RLfL%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fisx9L3RLfL%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSSU7Ei89r3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FSSU7Ei89r3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Reuters%20(%40Reuters)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FReuters%2Fstatus%2F1910028687267012804%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%209%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Canuck%2C%20whose%20alter%20ego%20is%20Tom%20Evans%2C%20is%20a%20Mountie%20-%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Royal%20Canadian%20Mounted%20Police%20-%20who%20gained%20his%20special%20powers%20after%20an%20alien%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'SUPERVILLAIN%20TRUMP%20AND%20HIS%20SIDEKICK%20MUSK'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20days%20of%20taking%20office%2C%20President%20Trump%20had%20managed%20to%20evoke%20an%20anti-American%20sentiment%20among%20Canadians%20and%20a%20feeling%20of%20resentment%20for%20him.%20It%20all%20started%20when%20he%20called%20the%20Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20%26quot%3BGovernor%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20followed%20that%20up%20with%20a%20threat%20to%20annex%20US'%20larger%20northern%20neighbour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Trump%2C%20who%20now%20finds%20himself%20as%20a%20supervillain%20in%20Canadian%20comic%20books%20and%20a%20graphic%20novel-based%20animated%20series%2C%20had%20offered%20to%20%26quot%3Bbuy%26quot%3B%20Canada%2C%20to%20which%20the%20Canadian%20government%20swiftly%20made%20a%20counter-offer%20to%20purchase%20the%20US%20state%20of%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20most%20of%20his%20press%20briefings%2C%20President%20Trump%20started%20referring%20to%20Canada%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%2051st%20state%26quot%3B%2C%20justifying%20how%20that%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20great%20move%26quot%3B%20to%20ensure%20better%20national%20security%20for%20%26quot%3Ball%20Americans%26quot%3B%20while%20also%20be%20economically%20wise%20for%20Canadians.%20This%20led%20to%20widespread%20protests%20against%20Trump%20with%20posters%20and%20placards%20reading%20%26quot%3BCanada%20Not%20For%20Sale!%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20Canada%2C%20President%20Trump%20was%20behaving%20just%20like%20a%20classic%20graphic%20novel%20'supervillain'%20-%20refusing%20to%20let%20go%20-%20in%20this%20case%2C%20of%20his%20rhetoric%20of%20wanting%20to%20annex%20Canada.%20He%20imposed%20punitive%20tariffs%20-%20first%20at%20a%20bilateral%20level%20across%20several%20industries%20and%20sectors%20-%20and%20then%20announce%20further%20%26quot%3Breciprocal%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20and%20some%20non-reciprocal%20ones%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20crush%20Canada%20economically.%20So%20great%20was%20the%20pressure%20that%20Canada's%20interim%20prime%20minister%20called%20for%20sudden%20snap%20polls%20in%20order%20to%20bring%20a%20decisive%20government%20with%20a%20strong%20mandate%20to%20counter%20Donald%20Trump's%20threats%20and%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20now%2C%20Canada%2C%20an%20immediate%20neighbour%20of%20the%20United%20States%20and%20one%20of%20its%20closest%20allies%20for%20many%20decades%2C%20distanced%20itself.%20The%20two%20governments%20went%20from%20being%20friends%20to%20foes%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks.%20Canadians%20never%20felt%20more%20strongly%20that%20the%20American%20leadership%20couldn't%20be%20trusted%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECanadians%2C%20who%20take%20pride%20in%20their%20%26quot%3Bliberal%20values%20and%20views%26quot%3B%20also%20despised%20the%20way%20Elon%20Musk%20was%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Binterfering%26quot%3B%20in%20government%20beyond%20the%20United%20States.%20Some%20even%20cited%20Musk's%20moves%20to%20reportedly%20back%20the%20right-wing%20and%20the%20far-right%20in%20Europe%20as%20an%20example%20of%20his%20intentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20like%20in%20some%20classic%20comic%20books%2C%20Musk%20was%20portrayed%20as%20'supervillain'%20Trump's%20sidekick%20-%20both%20of%20whom%20are%20shown%20being%20graphically%20manhandled%20and%20thrown%20out%20by%20superhero%20Captain%20Canuck.%20While%20in%20one%20frame%2C%20the%20comic%20shows%20Donald%20Trump%20being%20physically%20stopped%20by%20Captain%20Canuck%2C%20in%20another%20chapter%2C%20it%20shows%20Trump%20and%20Musk%20being%20dragged%20by%20the%20collar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Canuck%20was%20back%20in%20action%20-%20and%20an%20instant%20hit%20across%20Canada.%20Stores%20and%20libraries%20have%20their%20shelves%20stacked%20up%2C%20and%20Canadians%20seen%20lining%20up%20to%20get%20a%20copy%20for%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECANADA%20NEEDED%20AN%20ICON%20-%20IN%20THE%201970s%20AND%20NOW%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Comely%2C%20the%20co-creator%20of%20the%20superhero%2C%20said%20he%20created%20the%20character%20in%20the%201970s%20-%20at%20a%20moment%20when%20he%20thought%20Canadians%20wanted%20their%20own%20icon%2C%20given%20that%20the%20United%20States%20had%20Captain%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20was%20an%20undercurrent%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20in%20Canada%20in%20the%20'70s.%20So%20I%20think%20Canadians%20were%20starting%20to%20feel%20like%2C%20you%20know%2C%20like%20they%20should%20acknowledge%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20had%20our%20own%20country%2C%20and%20we%20had%20our%20own%20culture%20and%20be%20proud%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20were%20Canadians%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Comely%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20first%20publication%20in%201975%2C%20there%20have%20been%204%20million%20Captain%20Canuck-themed%20comic%20books%2C%20books%2C%20and%20graphic%20novels%20in%20print%20worldwide%2C%20Mr%20Comely%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20original%20storyline%20envisioned%20Canada%20as%20a%20world%20power%20that%20faces%20challenges%20from%2