mazon%20is%20applying%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20onslaught%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-shoppers-buying-ahead-stockpiling-price-increases-likely-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etariffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20vendors%20import%20their%20products%20from%20China%2C%20and%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-backs-off-retaliatory-tariffs-90-days-china-increase-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%20tariffs%20on%20goods%20from%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20increase%20to%20125%25.%20The%20vendors%20said%20Amazon%20likely%20doesn't%20want%20to%20risk%20losing%20the%20products%20they%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20vendors%20wholesale%20their%20products%20to%20Amazon%2C%20which%20then%20resells%20them%20on%20its%20online%20marketplace.%20Vendors%20account%20for%20roughly%2040%25%20of%20the%20products%20sold%20on%20Amazon%2C%20while%20the%20other%2060%25%20come%20from%20third-party%20merchants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmazon%20is%20not%20willing%20to%20suffer%20a%20mass%20exodus%20of%20vendors%20all%20at%20once%2C%26quot%3B%20Matt%20Daubenspeck%2C%20director%20of%20Apothecary%20Products%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIf%20customers%20cannot%20find%20what%20they%20want%20on%20Amazon%2C%20they%20may%20shop%20elsewhere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20price%20concessions%20are%20rarely%20available%20outside%20the%20normal%20price%20negotiation%20cycles%20and%20are%20only%20offered%20during%20extenuating%20circumstances%2C%20like%20the%20recent%20pandemic%20or%20a%20supply%20chain%20crisis%2C%20several%20vendors%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20offer%20isn't%20available%20to%20every%20vendor%2C%20and%20in%20most%20cases%2C%20Amazon%20requires%20margin%20guarantees%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20spokesperson%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229e03d617-7e69-4095-8d16-4b206651077d%5C