or%20everyone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20isn't%20extending%20the%20pricing%20increase%20to%20every%20vendor.%20Several%20vendors%20told%20BI%20their%20requests%20for%20a%20price%20change%20have%20been%20rejected%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20email%20seen%20by%20BI%2C%20an%20Amazon%20employee%20told%20a%20vendor%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bunable%20to%20accept%26quot%3B%20the%20price%20increase%20proposal%20and%20suggested%20exploring%20other%20cost-saving%20options.%20The%20email%20said%20the%20general%20manufacturing%20capacity%20in%20China%20is%20%26quot%3Bcurrently%20underutilized%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20factor%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20cost%20reductions%20for%20suppliers.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20said%20alternative%20cost-cutting%20measures%20and%20Chinese%20government%20subsidies%20are%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20passing%20increased%20costs%20to%20retail%20partners%2C%20we%20expect%20our%20vendors%20to%20thoroughly%20explore%20and%20implement%20all%20possible%20operational%20efficiencies%20and%20cost-reduction%20strategies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20email%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20vendors%20told%20BI%20that%20it's%20unclear%20what%20criteria%20Amazon%20follows%20before%20accepting%20price%20increase%20requests.%20It%20appears%20Amazon%20wants%20to%20keep%20the%20process%20opaque%20for%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20not%20cite%20out%20internal%20policies%26quot%3B%20when%20rejecting%20a%20vendor's%20request%2C%20the%20internal%20document%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETruist%20Securities%20managing%20director%20Youssef%20Squali%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Thursday%20that%20he%20is%20lowering%20Amazon's%20growth%20estimates%20in%20part%20due%20to%20tariff-driven%20price%20hikes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20there%20are%20several%20currents%20and%20countercurrents%20hurting%20and%20benefiting%20Amazon%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20believe%20the%20net%20net%20of%20this%20is%20an%20in