0in%20the%20line%20of%20fire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRajita%20and%20I%20were%20at%20the%20Taj%20at%20the%20Masala%20Craft%20restaurant.%20One%20of%20our%20friends%2C%20a%20German%20member%20of%20the%20European%20Parliament%2C%20was%20visiting%20with%20a%20big%20parliamentary%20delegation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20just%20starting%20dinner%20at%20about%209%3A30%20pm%2C%20the%20first%20firing%20started%2C%20and%20I%20just%20looked%20out%20and%20I%20saw%20somebody%20shooting%20into%20the%20Golden%20Dragon%20restaurant%2C%20which%20is%20about%2030%20meters%20from%20where%20we%20were.%20Luckily%2C%20that%20door%20used%20to%20look%20like%20a%20steel%20wall%2C%20and%20there%20was%20no%20latch%20inside.%20I%20just%20tied%20up%20the%20door%20with%20napkins%2C%20tableware%2C%20and%20people%20were%20not%20ready%20to%20move.%20We%20were%20told%20there%20is%20a%20shooting%20outside.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20more%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-rana-26-11-mumbai-terror-attacks-bringing-back-memories-survivor-spots-herself-in-ndtvs-26-11-footage-8130472%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BBringing%20Back%20Memories%26quot%3B%3A%20Survivor%20Spots%20Herself%20In%20NDTV's%2026%2F11%20Footage%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagga%20told%20NDTV%20that%20his%20friend%20had%20been%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-rana-extradition-live-updates-tahawwur-rana-26-11-terror-attack-mastermind-enroute-india-8130363%5C%22%3Eterror%20hostage%20situation%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20Sri%20Lanka%20earlier.%20So%20she%20was%20well%20trained%20and%20told%20them%20that%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20now%20becoming%20a%20hostage%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'People%20Killed%20On%20Both%20Sides'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagga%20and%20his%20wife%20were%20spotted%20in%20the%20NDTV%20footage%20from%2016%20years%20ago%2C%20which%20was%20taken%20shortly%20after%20the%20firing%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20both%20sides%2C%20there%20were%20people%20killed.%20On%20the%20right%20was%20the%20Shamiana%2024%2F7%20coffee%20shop%2C%20and%20on%20the%20left%20was%20Golden%20Dragon.%20There%20was%20nobody%20who%20survived.%20Everyone%20was%20killed%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bagga%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20providentially%20safe%20in%20Masala%20Craft.%20And%20then%20after%20two%20hours%2C%20the%20hotel%20moved%20us%20to%20the%20chambers%20through%20the%20basement%20area%20of%20the%20staff%20entrance.%20We%20were%20moved%20out%20to%20the%20chambers%2C%20and%20we%20were%20there.%20About%20200%20people%20were%20there.%20%C2%A0A%20politician%20gave%20a%20media%20interview%2C%20and%20he%20said%20200%20CEOs%20and%20very%20senior%20people%20of%20Mumbai%20are%20trapped%20here%20in%20chambers...%20They%20entered%20chambers%20and%20opened%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20then%2C%20our%20evacuation%20started%20from%20the%20fire%20escape.%20One%20old%20woman%20fell.%20I%20bent%20down%20to%20pick%20her%20up%2C%20and%20I%20told%20my%20wife%20that%20we%20would%20not%20push.%20People%20were%20pushing%20and%20running%20down.%20I%20said%2C%20we'll%20not%20push.%20We'll%20wait%20for%20our%20turn%2C%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20in%20front%20of%20us%2C%20there%20was%20nobody%20alive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Taj%20Staffer%20Saved%20Our%20Life'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagga%2C%20who%20was%20stuck%20in%20the%20Chambers%20and%20was%20awaiting%20his%20turn%20to%20get%20rescued%2C%20said%20a%20staff%20member%20from%20the%20Taj%20saved%20his%20and%20his%20wife's%20lives.%20Mr%20Bagga%20said%2C%20the%20staffer%20%26quot%3BTook%20bullets%20in%20his%20back%20and%20we%20hid%20in%20a%20conference%20room%2C%20lying%20on%20the%20ground%20for%20the%20next%20about%20seven%20hours.%20Through%20the%20night%2C%20he%20(the%20staffer)%20was%20crying.%20We%20had%20nothing%20but%20aspirin%20and%20whatever%20people%20had.%20There%20were%20two%20doctors%20with%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20tied%20up%20his%20wounds%20as%20well%20as%20we%20could%2C%20and%20he%20made%20it%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20but%20he%20did%20not%20survive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20all%20lying%20down%20in%20the%20room%20and%20the%20other%20conference%20rooms.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20over%20because%20huge%20smoke%20started%20coming%20in.%20They%20were%20throwing%20grenades%20from%20the%20top%20to%20try%20to%20break%20the%20building...very%20heavy%20smoke%20came%20in%2C%20and%20we%20couldn't%20breathe.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20over%20because%20there%20was%20a%20flimsy%20door%20between%20us%20and%20them%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20National%20Security%20Guard%20(NSG)%20came%20at%2010%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Bagga%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20gunfight%20continued%20between%20the%20commandos%20and%20the%20terrorists%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bsomehow%20the%20god%20was%20kind%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20was%20out%20of%20the%20danger%20zone%20by%2010%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'We%20Hugged%20Taj%20Employees%20Who%20Survived'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagga%20said%20he%20had%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20Taj%20hotel%20after%20a%20month%20since%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20chambers%20and%20relive%20the%20near-death%20experience%20he%20had%20inside%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20through%20the%20entire%20route%20that%20we%20had%20taken%2C%20right%20from%20Masala%20Craft%2C%20through%20the%20basement%2C%20the%20staff%20entrances%2C%20and%20to%20the%20chambers.%20And%20we%20went%20and%20hugged%20all%20the%20employees%20who%20survived.%20A%20lot%20of%20Taj%20employees%20gave%20up%20their%20lives%20to%20save%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20that%20when%20the%20NSG%20came%20to%20their%20rescue%2C%20they%20didn't%20know%20if%20it's%20the%20terrorists%20pretending%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Black%20Cat%20commandos%20or%20it's%20really%20the%20NSG%20but%20then%20they%20said%2C%20stand%20back.%20We%20are%20breaking%20through.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(NSG)%20had%20to%20break%20the%20door%20because%20we%20had%20tied%20it%20up%20with%20all%20the%20tablecloths.%20There%20were%20no%20latches%20in%20any%20of%20the%20doors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bagga's%20wife%2C%20Ranjita%20Kulkarni%2C%20also%20spoke%20to%20NDTV%20and%20said%2C%20The%20extradition%20of%20Rana%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bmonumental%20achievement%20for%20our%20country%26quot%3B.%20She%20thanked%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%2C%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20the%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20for%20making%20this%20possible.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20quite%20sure%20it%20will%20bring%20justice.%20This%20is%20a%20huge%20day%20for%20all%20martyrs%20who%20sacrificed%20their%20lives%2C%20survivors%20and%20their%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F26-11-accused-tahawwur-rana-extradited-from-us-on-a-special-flight-lands-in-delhi-8133460%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETahawwaur%20Rana's%20Role%20In%2026%2F11%20Attacks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Pakistan%20Army%20doctor%20provided%20logistic%2C%20financial%20and%20other%20assistance%20to%20David%20Headley%20--%20a%20key%20conspirator%20in%20the%20terror%20attack.%20Rana%20is%20charged%20under%20sections%20relating%20to%20criminal%20conspiracy%2C%20waging%20war%20against%20the%20government%20of%20India%2C%20murder%20and%20forgery%20and%20relevant%20sections%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20(Prevention)%20Act.%20He%20also%20travelled%20to%20various%20places%20in%20India%20as%20they%20identified%20targets%20to%20strike%2C%20the%20chargesheet%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publishe