0the%20successful%20extradition%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20mastermind%20Tahawwur%20Hussain%20Rana%20to%20India%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20important%26quot%3B%20as%20his%20interrogation%20could%20help%20in%20filling%20the%20blanks%20left%20behind%20from%20earlier%20investigations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENIA's%20former%20inspector%20general%20Loknath%20Behera%20told%20NDTV%20the%20case%20against%20Rana%20which%20is%20being%20handled%20by%20the%20anti-terror%20agency%20is%20related%20to%20a%20larger%20conspiracy%20and%20is%20pending%20before%20a%20special%20NIA%20court%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20NIA%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20Rana%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20second%20case%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20against%20Rana%20in%202023%20for%20plotting%20the%2026%2F11%20terror%20attacks%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20differences%20%5Bbetween%20the%20two%20cases%5D.%20The%20NIA%20case%20is%20related%20to%20a%20conspiracy%20much%20larger%20and%20beyond%20the%20Mumbai%20attack%20cases%20because%20these%20people%20were%20also%20wrecking%20other%20places%2C%20including%20National%20Defence%20College%2C%20etc.%20And%20there%20were%20probably%20bigger%20game%20plans.%20Some%20of%20them%20are%20yet%20to%20be%20revealed.%20Therefore%2C%20this%20extradition%20assumes%20more%20importance%20because%20we%20never%20got%20access%20to%20Rana%20to%20be%20interrogated%20just%20like%20we%20did%20in%20respect%20of%20Headley%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Behera%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20David%20Headman%20Coley%2C%20a%20Pakistan-born%20US%20citizen%20who%20ran%20reconnaissance%20of%20civilian%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Behera%20said%20unless%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20merges%20these%20two%20cases%20and%20transfers%20to%20a%20special%20court%2C%20there%20will%20be%20two%20trials%20-%20one%20in%20Delhi%2C%20the%20other%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I'm%20sure%20he%20%5BRana%5D%20knows%20certain%20things%20which%20we%20do%20not%20know.%20And%20probably%20that%20will%20be%20actually%20more%20revealing.%20And%20I%20will%20not%20be%20surprised%20to%20see%20that%20more%20names%20come%20out.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20know%20the%20handlers%20of%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20but%20who%20are%20the%20handlers%20of%20Rana%3F%20Maybe%20they%20are%20the%20same%20or%20they%20are%20different.%20So%20all%20these%20questions%20were%20there%20during%20our%20investigation%2C%20but%20we%20could%20not%20answer%20them%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20this%20person%20%5BRana%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20NIA%20officer%20said.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20we%20are%20in%20a%20better%20position%20and%20it%20is%20actually%20a%20victory%20of%20diplomacy%2C%20the%20concerted%20effort%20of%20all%20the%20agencies%2C%20the%20government%20and%20various%20departments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2Fep4u6pf_rana_625x300_10_April_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20about%20whether%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%20got%20away%2C%20Mr%20Behera%20said%20Indian%20investigators%20could%20question%20Headley%20owing%20to%20effective%20diplomacy%20and%20good%20ties%20with%20the%20US%2C%20and%20he%20did%20not%20go%20scot-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20two%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20FBI%20in%202009...%20Thanks%20to%20the%20good%20work%2C%20we%20actually%20could%20examine%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%20and%20get%20some%20information.%20But%20that%20did%20not%20happen%20in%20respect%20of%20Rana.%20So%20that%20is%20the%20one%20part%20of%20this.%20But%20in%20the%20process%2C%20what%20happened%20is%20that%20Headley%20invoked%20plea%20bargaining%20with%20the%20court%20concerned%20in%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20that%20plea%20bargaining%2C%20he%20will%20not%20be%20extradited%20to%20any%20country%2C%20including%20India%2C%20or%20in%20Denmark%2C%20or%20some%20other%20places%2C%20wherever%20there%20is%20a%20case.%20So%20anything%20you%20want%20to%20do%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20done%20on%20American%20soil.%20He%20cannot%20be%20extradited%20as%20on%20date%2C%20as%20per%20the%20law%20now.%20If%20something%20changes%20subsequently%2C%20I%20do%20not%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhereas%20Rana%20was%20sentenced%20to%2014%20years%20imprisonment%20in%20the%20Denmark%20case%2C%20and%20acquitted%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20case...%20I%20believe%2C%20I%20personally%20am%20very%20convinced%20that%20Rana%20will%20tell%20something%20which%20will%20be%20very%20relevant%2C%20and%20maybe%20more%20information%20than%20we%20know.%20So%20it%20is%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Behera%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20arriving%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Rana%20was%20taken%20for%20a%20medical%20test%20and%20produced%20before%20the%20court%20of%20special%20NIA%20judge%20Chander%20Jit%20Singh%2C%20who%20heard%20his%20custody%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20lawyer%20Dayan%20Krishnan%20and%20special%20public%20prosecutor%20Narender%20Mann%20represented%20the%20NIA.%20Lawyer%20Piyush%20Sachdeva%20from%20Delhi%20Legal%20Services%20Authority%20represented%20Rana.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744308600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-04%2F2ekdmrqk_loknath-behra_625x300_10_April_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-rana-may-reveal-more-names-ex-anti-terror-agency-nia-official-loknath-behra-8135441%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20former%20top%20official%20of%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20termed%20the%20successful%20extradition%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20mastermind%20Tahawwur%20Hussain%20Rana%20to%20India%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20important%26quot%3B%20as%20his%20inter