%20The%20Helm%20Of%20NIA%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fndtv.in%2Findia%2Fnia-chief-sadanand-date-who-was-injured-by-kasabs-hand-grenade-8129857%5C%22%3E1990-batch%20IPS%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Maharashtra%20cadre%2C%20Sadanand%20Date's%20journey%20in%20the%20Indian%20police%20is%20nothing%20short%20of%20inspiring.%20Born%20into%20a%20humble%20household%2C%20Mr%20Date%20spent%20his%20childhood%20delivering%20newspapers%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%20His%20mother%20worked%20as%20a%20domestic%20helper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20long%20career%2C%20Mr%20Date%20has%20served%20in%20key%20positions%20across%20Mumbai%20Police%20and%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI).%20His%20stints%20have%20included%20heading%20the%20Maharashtra%20Anti-Terrorism%20Squad%20and%20being%20appointed%20the%20first%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20for%20the%20Mira-Bhayandar-Vasai-Virar%20region.%20In%202023%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20many%2C%20Mr%20Date's%20name%20remains%20synonymous%20with%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks%2C%20as%20he%20fought%20on%20the%20frontline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisplay%20Of%20Valour%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2026%2C%202008%2C%20around%209%3A30%20pm%20Mumbai%20plunged%20into%20chaos.%20While%20the%20attack%20unfolded%20outside%20his%20jurisdiction%2C%20Mr%20Date%20-%20then%20Additional%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%2C%20Central%20Region%20-%20didn't%20hesitate.%20From%20his%20home%20in%20Malabar%20Hill%2C%20he%20rushed%20out%20to%20the%20CST%20railway%20station.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20he%20stopped%20at%20a%20police%20station%2C%20armed%20himself%20with%20a%20carbine%2C%20and%20took%20six%20officers%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20CST%2C%20he%20learnt%20the%20terrorists%20had%20moved%20towards%20Cama%20and%20Albless%20Hospital%2C%20a%20facility%20for%20women%20and%20children.%20Fearing%20a%20possible%20hostage%20situation%2C%20MrDate%20led%20his%20team%20straight%20to%20the%20hospital%20complex.%20He%20soon%20spotted%20the%20attackers%20firing%20from%20the%20rooftop%20and%20returned%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20trying%20to%20enter%20the%20hospital%20building%2C%20Mr%20Date%20was%20caught%20in%20the%20blast%20of%20a%20grenade%20thrown%20by%20Kasab.%20The%20grenade%20exploded%20just%20three%20feet%20away%2C%20according%20to%20reports.%20The%20explosion%20killed%20Sub-Inspector%20Prakash%20More%20and%20left%20Mr%20Date%20and%20three%20other%20officers%20injured.%20Despite%20his%20wounds%2C%20he%20chose%20to%20remain%20on%20the%20spot%2C%20instructing%20his%20injured%20colleagues%20to%20seek%20medical%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHolding%20The%20Line%20For%2040%20Minutes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Date%20continued%20the%20operation%20with%20the%20remaining%20officers.%20They%20climbed%20up%20to%20the%20sixth%20floor%2C%20just%20beneath%20the%20terrace%20where%20the%20terrorists%20were%20positioned.%20Stationing%20himself%20by%20the%20staircase%2C%20the%20officer%20exchanged%20fire%20for%20nearly%2040%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20danger%20hadn't%20passed.%20Another%20grenade%20landed%20near%20him.%20The%20shrapnel%20pierced%20his%20legs%20and%20face%2C%20causing%20profuse%20bleeding.%20In%20the%20chaos%2C%20Kasab%20and%20Ismail%20managed%20to%20escape.%20But%20Mr%20Date%20and%20his%20team%20had%20bought%20precious%20time%20and%20kept%20the%20terrorists%20from%20launching%20further%20attacks%20in%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20courage%20that%20night%2C%20Sadanand%20Date%20was%20awarded%20the%20President's%20Police%20Medal%20for%20Gallantry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744275900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ft3fou3ho_sadanand-vasant-date-1200_625x300_28_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-sadanand-date-26-11