nd-on-tariffs-13345606%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UP%20Man%20Helps%20Restore%20Dal%20Lake%E2%80%99s%20Beauty%20by%20Creating%20Organic%20Fertiliser%20Using%20Weeds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhat%20may%20have%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F318930%2Fhomestays-in-srinagar-kashmir-scenic-views-of-dal-lake-mughal-tulip-gardens-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecasual%20vacation%20to%20Kashmir%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20wife%20to%20celebrate%20their%20first%20wedding%20anniversary%20in%202013%20turned%20into%20a%20vision%20for%20Maninder%20Singh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurrounded%20by%20the%20majestic%20mountains%20of%20Kashmir%2C%20Dal%20Lake%20is%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20iconic%20and%20picturesque%20destinations.%20Its%20serene%20waters%2C%20dotted%20with%20%3Cem%3Eshikaras%20%3C%2Fem%3E(boats)%20and%20framed%20by%20willow%20trees%2C%20attract%20countless%20visitors%20each%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20beneath%20its%20tranquil%20surface%2C%20the%20lake%20faces%20a%20persistent%20environmental%20crisis%3A%20the%20overgrowth%20of%20lake%20weeds.%20For%20decades%2C%20this%20issue%20has%20affected%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20natural%20beauty%2C%20with%20no%20effective%20solution%20in%20sight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20trip%2C%20Maninder%20(41)%20first%20encountered%20the%20lake%20weeds%20%E2%80%94%20a%20sight%20that%20deeply%20disturbed%20him.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20weeds%20near%20Dal%20Lake%2C%20I%20wondered%2C%20where%20do%20these%20go%20once%20they%20pile%20up.%20The%20lake%E2%80%99s%20beauty%20was%20being%20marred%20by%20this%20seemingly%20useless%20