ral-sundargarh-odisha-empower-women%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20management%20issue%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Dal%20Lake%20but%20also%20offers%20a%20replicable%20model%20for%20other%20lake%20conservation%20projects.%20The%20initiative%20has%20had%20a%20positive%20environmental%20impact%20by%20converting%20lake%20biomass%20into%20bio-manure%2C%20contributing%20to%20both%20conservation%20efforts%20and%20agricultural%20sustainability%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGreener%20lakes%2C%20stronger%20communities%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20environmental%20impact%2C%20CEF%20Group%20has%20made%20strides%20in%20managing%20the%20excess%20lake%20weed.%20Between%20August%20and%20December%202024%2C%20they%20received%20a%20total%20of%2014%2C864%20tonnes%20of%20lake%20weed.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%204%2C131%20tonnes%20were%20converted%20into%20organic%20manure%2C%20a%20process%20that%20has%20led%20to%20a%20reduction%20of%20approximately%202%2C891%20tonnes%20of%20CO%E2%82%82%20emissions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20perspective%2C%20converting%20just%20one%20tonne%20of%20lake%20weed%20into%20organic%20manure%20results%20in%20a%20CO2%20savings%20of%20around%200.7%20tonnes.%20%E2%80%9COur%20project%20is%20designed%20to%20process%20up%20to%2070%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20lake%20weed%20each%20year%2C%20which%20yields%20between%2020%2C000%20to%2022%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20organic%20manure.%20This%20large-scale%20effort%20is%20expected%20to%20lead%20to%20an%20annual%20reduction%20of%20around%2050%2C000%20tonnes%20of%20CO%E2%82%82%20emissions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Maninder%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20aspect%20of%20this%20process%20is%20the%20leachate%20treatment%2C%20which%20involves%20the%20water%20that%20is%20extracted%20from%20the%20lake%20weeds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20lake%20weeds%20is%20carefully%20treated%20to%20remove%20any%20harmful%20contaminants%20like%20heavy%20metals%2C