una%20and%20insects%20into%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20plantation%20drives%20are%20conducted%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20he%20says%20the%20project%E2%80%99s%20impact%20on%20the%20local%20communities%20has%20been%20telling.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20plantation%20drives%20have%20created%20temporary%20employment%20opportunities%2C%20particularly%20for%20marginalised%20groups%2C%20in%20nursery%20management%2C%20plantation%2C%20and%20upkeep.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollaborating%20with%20CATCH%20Foundation%20meant%20that%20the%20team%20at%20NSG%20was%20in%20constant%20touch%20with%20the%20land%E2%80%99s%20progress.%20Sharing%20that%20transparency%20is%20a%20mainstay%20of%20their%20approach%2C%20Bharat%20says%20their%20three-level%20monitoring%20system%20makes%20this%20possible.%20%E2%80%9COur%20environmental%20protectors%20see%20to%20the%20upkeep%20of%20the%20plot%20and%20report%20to%20the%20maintenance%20in%20charge%2C%20who%20then%20report%20to%20the%20forest%20conservation%20managers.%20This%20ensures%20that%20the%20company%20knows%20everything%20about%20their%20plot%20and%20how%20it%20is%20doing.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20a%20mobile%20app%20that%20can%20be%20accessed%20by%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20which%20is%20used%20to%20assess%20on-ground%20activities.%20Transparency%20is%20a%20benchmark%20in%20this%20industry.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-3_11zon-174420