%99s%20competitive%20journey%20reached%20new%20heights%20in%202023%20when%20she%20entered%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F32273%2Fmohammad-iftekhar-khan-in-kickboxing-nationals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENational%20Kickboxing%20Championship%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20first%20time%20and%20secured%20two%20gold%20medals.%20This%20momentum%20carried%20her%20into%202024%2C%20a%20year%20packed%20with%20international%20challenges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFacing%20a%20demanding%20schedule%2C%20with%20the%20WAKO%20World%20Cup%20before%20the%20Asian%20Kickboxing%20Championship%202024%2C%20she%20had%20virtually%20no%20time%20for%20specific%20preparation.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20performances%20I%20was%20giving%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20and%20Asian%20Championships%20were%20the%20same%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%20With%20two%20major%20events%20on%20the%20horizon%20and%20only%20three%20months%20to%20prepare%2C%20she%20dedicated%20herself%20to%20relentless%20training%2C%20sacrificing%20even%20her%20Sundays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiving%20us%20a%20glimpse%20of%20her%20routine%2C%20Shradhha%20shares%20that%20she%20starts%20her%20day%20with%20a%20five-hour%20training%20session%20from%205%20am%20to%2010%20am.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%2011%20am%20to%2012%20pm%2C%20I%20try%20to%20study%20during%20exams.%20In%20the%20afternoon%2C%20I%20have%20footwork%20or%20technical%20sessions%20from%201%20pm%20to%203%20pm.%20Post-lunch%2C%20I%20have%20one%20more%20session%20either%20in%20the%20gym%20or%20sparring%20(fighting)%20with%20my%20teammates%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T155759.360-1744021702.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shraddha%20with%20her%20achievements%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T155759.360-1744021702.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T155759.360-1744021702-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T155759.360-1744021702-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T155759.360-1744021702-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-04-07T155759.360-1744021702-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418303%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShraddha%E2%80%99s%20determination%20and%20hard%20work%20have%20helped%20her%20win%20medals%20in%20championships.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20occasionally%20train%20with%20Shraddha%20when%20she%20has%20an%20event%20coming%20up%20and%20when%20she%20requires%20a%20fight%20partner%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Ritij%20Rajput%2C%20a%20taekwondo%20athlete%20turned%20bodybuilder.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20that%20she%20creates%20her%20schedule%20and%20trains%20with%20determination%20is%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20success%20in%20the%20sport%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ritij%20adds%2C%20who%20has%20seen%20her%20taekwondo%20and%20kickboxing%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOvercoming%20the%20formidable%20competition%20requires%20%E2%80%9Cunwavering%20dedication%2C%20visualisation%2C%20training%2C%20and%20manifestation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CI%20only%20have%20one%20mantra%3A%20when%20there%20is%20a%20tournament%2C%20I%20look%20at%20the%20venue%20and%20picture%20it%20in%20my%20mind.%20I%20visualise%20myself%20in%20the%20venue%20and%20practice%20my%20routine%20again%20and%20again.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp